f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.040bf50b-10d0-4efa-b49b-1fa088dc47f3.prompt=Enter password\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.091a0a82-be87-4047-b819-0ec65fc5a4f6.prompt=Enter username\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.0a2b4190-a9b8-429d-bf73-24d524fcbfe3.prompt=Enter OU's Distinguished Name(DN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.0f8285f6-c41e-4532-98ec-c8e45a9df344.description=
Disables a computer account in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the computer is in (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
computerCommonName - the name of the computer (its CN)
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Responses\:
success - computer account was successfully disabled
failure - something went wrong

Extra Results\:
computerDN - The Distinguinsed Name of the computer account that was disabled.
f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.1168b74f-e390-4aa3-8c44-07e5f7f68205.prompt=Enter computer Common Name(CN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.1956664d-9b9e-497c-a78e-a0d024c441d6.prompt=Enter computer Distinguished Name(DN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.1eb51fb1-0e48-49c8-b4f2-8fe32ef80121.description=
Gets the name of the OU a computer account is in, in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
rootDN - the distinguished name of the root element whose subtree you want to search in
computerCommonName - the name of the computer account
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Returns\:
The name of the OU where the computer account is located.

Responses\:
success - The name of the OU the computer is in was retrieved successfully.
failure - Determining computer's OU failed.

Extra Results\:
oUDN - OU's distinguished name
f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.20b674e2-8215-49b0-8e94-b96bac092f8a.prompt=Enter password\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.26b62922-b15a-4ea3-8d81-1cbfb4fba77e.prompt=Enter password\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.28fb0a27-11a1-42af-a7a0-148b75a6d840.prompt=Enter username\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.294defd7-e38e-48a7-8bf6-ea7e40fc2739.prompt=Enter password\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.297a9dde-47ac-47c6-8c32-ac1ec2753f42.prompt=Enter host\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.2ce34782-2f78-4c4b-92ef-513a269b877f.prompt=Enter host\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.2d339005-fa7f-4c81-9609-0517dc2162ae.description=
Creates a new computer account in Active Directory.

Input Parameters\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN to add the computer to (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
computerCommonName - the name of the computer (its CN)
username - user to connect to AD as
password - password to connect to AD as

Responses\:
success - created new computer account in AD
failure - failed to create computer account

Extra Results\:
computerDN - the distinguished name of the newly created computer account
f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.3286d763-ee0d-43f2-a8e3-435378d60aad.description=
Checks to see if a computer account is enabled in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the computer is in (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
computerCommonName - the name of the computer account to check
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Responses\:
success - The computer account is enabled.
failure - The computer account is disabled or something went wrong.

Extra Results\:
computerDN - The Distinguinsed Name of the computer account.
f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.334fd3e9-9972-4db8-8bc2-52c823b59238.prompt=Enter computer Common Name(CN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.34b7fb85-d841-4779-9346-2c2857e6b06e.prompt=Enter host\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.37374556-6835-4b2b-bf07-5b4443a3e027.prompt=Enter root Distinguished Name (DN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.583968f4-755e-4fa1-b53e-773098c5946e.prompt=Enter host\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.58794032-6ef6-4271-afdb-d4c651ffc259.prompt=Enter computer Common Name(CN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.624ca990-443a-41d0-8526-b6ed3ed2c393.description=
Resets a computer account in Active Directory, by resetting the password to an initial password.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
computerDN - the distinguished name of the computer account we want to reset
username - the windows username to connect to Active Directory as
password - password for username

Responses\:
success - Computer account reseted successfully
failure - Failed to reset computer account
f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.667885a7-9fe2-4ae6-a7a0-0bf039b2bce8.prompt=Enter OU's Distinguished Name(DN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.7073eaf8-cdc9-4d92-bae5-832199a512ad.prompt=Enter computer Distinguished Name(DN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.7202eab8-d945-4a4f-a3ac-424c1780e4a5.prompt=Enter username\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.73907a05-3efe-4d03-8460-3e71dee145c4.prompt=Enter username\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.75b6bf29-69b3-416b-85c8-3c9411214dd8.prompt=Enter computer Common Name(CN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.84a7be4a-ce82-4a86-b766-b4eb0e8a0f73.description=
Moves a computer account in a new OU in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
computerDN - the distinguished name of the computer account we want to move
newOUDN - the Organizational Unit that the computer account will be moved to
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Returns\:
The new distinguished name (DN) of the computer account, after it was moved to the new OU.

Responses\:
success - Moving the computer account to a new OU was successful.
failure - Moving computer account to new OU failed.
f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.8e5c1a6b-429b-44a7-b729-35985101b373.prompt=Enter host\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.8f21a5be-e584-4306-b6c6-91b189cf49d3.prompt=Enter password\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.95d3846a-5731-48b7-8b2d-534292cdbcdd.prompt=Enter root Distinguished Name (DN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.9918a8aa-45d2-4a70-93b5-150e94c4bb63.prompt=Enter OU's Distinguished Name(DN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.9a342809-f366-4254-8b00-02c946319df5.prompt=Enter computer Common Name(CN)\: f7a80487-8efe-45a2-a1fe-4acf77878c10.a79aa340-1e05-4f34-a6a9-e940f25c84d2.description=
Deletes a computer account from Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the computer is in (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
computerCommonName - the name of the computer (its CN)
username - user to connect to AD as
password - password to connect to AD as

Responses\:
success - computer account was successfully deleted.
failure - failed to delete computer account.

Extra Results\:
computerDN - The Distinguinsed Name of the computer account that was deleted.

Creates a new computer account in Active Directory, performs some operations on it (disables and enables it, searches for its OU, moves it to another OU, resets it) and then deletes it.

Input Parameters\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
OU - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN to add the computer to (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
computerCommonName - the name of the computer (its CN)
rootDN - the distinguished name of the root element whose subtree you want to search in
newOUDN - the Organizational Unit that the computer account will be moved to
username - user to connect to AD as
password - password to connect to AD as

Responses\:
success - all operations finished successfully
failure - failed to do some operation
